\begin_inset Newpage pagebreak
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
5.
 IT neuronal responses are reduced by the presence of multiple objects in
 limited clutter conditions and are well predicted by the average of their
 responses to constituent objects.
 [Zoccolan, 2005]
